whereas.text:
Whereas, generally, little is known about late-stage
			 treatment of asbestos-related diseases, and there is no cure for such
			 diseases;

Whereas early detection of asbestos-related diseases may
			 give some patients increased treatment options and might improve their
			 prognoses;

Whereas a significant percentage of all asbestos-related
			 disease victims were exposed to asbestos on naval ships and in
			 shipyards;

Whereas asbestos was used in the construction of a
			 significant number of office buildings and public facilities built before
			 1975;

paragraph.text:
designates the
			 first week of April 2013 as National Asbestos Awareness
			 Week;
